Merges class names using clsx and tailwind-merge. Handles conditional classes and deduplication.

```tsx
import { cn } from "@/lib/utils";
cn("px-2 py-1", condition && "bg-blue-500", "text-white");
```

Creates variant-based class name functions using class-variance-authority.

```tsx
const buttonVariants = cva("inline-flex items-center", {
  variants: {
    variant: { default: "bg-primary", destructive: "bg-destructive" },
    size: { default: "h-10 px-4", sm: "h-9 px-3" },
  },
  defaultVariants: { variant: "default", size: "default" },
});
```

